  <h1>Nature Play <span class="it">&amp; Inquiry</span></h1>
  <p class="cover-subtitle">Supports early mathematical set counting, attribute classification, and spatial tracking through the tactile manipulation of geometric timber shapes and natural textures.</p>

  <div class="footer">
