  <p style="margin: 22px auto 0; max-width: 62ch; font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--ink-soft);">The Papoose felt loose parts are hand-felted from wool in Nepal, WFTO &amp; Fair Trade USA Certified. The teak nature tools are hand-finished from SVLK teak in Indonesia. The Wild Mountain Child tools are carved from FSC-certified Doussie in Vietnam. We accept a limited number of classroom orders each season, so the work stays true. Reserve early.</p>
