        <div class="p"><span class="label">Practical Life</span><p>Scooping, pouring, pincer grip, the slow rhythm of the work.</p></div>
        <div class="p"><span class="label">Outdoor Learning</span><p>From garden to nature table to mud kitchen and back.</p></div>
        <div class="p"><span class="label">NGSS &middot; K&ndash;2</span><p>Life science, classification, place-based observation.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
